high_descs: Turn left and walk forward, then hang a left and walk up to the fridge, turn left and walk over to the wall then turn left and walk up to the round black table.
Pick up the black bowl off of the round black table.
Walk around the round black table to the fridge.
Put the black bowl in the fridge and close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the now chilled black bowl, then close the fridge.
Walk over to the kitchen sink.
Put the chilled black bowl in the leftmost sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled black bowl in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and step to your right then walk to the fridge then turn left and walk to the wall then turn left and step to the table.
Pick up the bowl that's in front of you near the butter knife.
Turn left and step to your left then walk to the counter then turn left to face the fridge.
Chill the bowl in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn around and take a step then turn left and walk to the sink then turn left to face it.
Put the bowl in the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold bowl in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the fridge, then left to the wall, and turn left to face the round table.
Pick up the dark bowl from the table.
Turn to your left and go to the fridge.
Chill the bowl in the fridge, then take it out.
Go to the sink that is to the right of the fridge.
Put the bowl in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl into the sink.
